    {
      "id": "90b51363-d5fc-4472-b50e-99596b15a502",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Results show that the performance of a predictive model is related with the number of significant features, the number of categories of the significant features and, more particularly, the Spearman Correlation Coefficients for the significant features. ",
